summary: Mid-Level Marketing Manager with 5 years of experience in digital campaigns.
long_summary: John has led cross-channel marketing initiatives at two Fortune 500 firms and one tech startup. He specializes in SEO, PPC, and content marketing strategies that drive lead generation. He recently managed a $1M ad budget and achieved a 25% increase in monthly qualified leads. John holds an MBA from Northwestern University. He is adept at data analysis, A/B testing, and marketing automation tools.
